413
00:17:57,540 --> 00:17:59,520
 oko 20 do 30 ljudi

414
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:00,600
 preko interneta,

415
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:01,640
 preko YouTube-a.

416
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:03,740
 I u početku smo molili

417
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:04,580
 prije mjesec dana

418
00:18:04,580 --> 00:18:05,480
 u četiri jutro,

419
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:06,760
 kasnije smo pomjerili

420
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:07,540
 u pet jutro,

421
00:18:07,540 --> 00:18:08,260
 pa u šest,

422
00:18:08,260 --> 00:18:09,300
 ali htio sam

423
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:10,880
 da bude natopljeno žrtvom,

424
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,640
 jer znam da me čeka

425
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:13,540
 težak put,

426
00:18:13,540 --> 00:18:14,980
 ma meni je na kraju

427
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:16,120
 bilo najlakše hodat.

428
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:17,360
 Meni je bilo

429
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:18,240
 najteže molit,

430
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:19,880
 jer ti ulaziš

431
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,340
 sa Isom

432
00:18:20,340 --> 00:18:21,620
 u jako osjetljivo područje,

433
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,240
 u rane rata.

434
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:24,460
 Ali vjerujte mi,

435
00:18:24,460 --> 00:18:26,980
 kada ideš sa gospodinom,

436
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:27,940
 onda se ne trebaš

437
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:28,540
 bojati ničega.

438
00:18:28,540 --> 00:18:30,580
 I nakon 100-15 dana

439
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:31,080
 molitve,

440
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:31,640
 stvarno,

441
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:33,140
 svako jutro sam bio ustrajan,

442
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,240
 Bog mi je dao milost

443
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,780
 i to mi je bilo

444
00:18:35,780 --> 00:18:36,400
 najbitnije,

445
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:37,520
 jer dobra priprema

446
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:38,340
 je pola posla.

447
00:18:38,340 --> 00:18:40,180
 Dobra priprema

448
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:40,920
 je pola posla.

449
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:42,440
 Nakon toga

450
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:42,960
 sam stupio

451
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,380
 u kontakt

452
00:18:43,380 --> 00:18:44,500
 sa nanomom rođenima

453
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:45,300
 i rekao im

454
00:18:45,300 --> 00:18:45,780
 da sam dobio

455
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:47,300
 pocaj na ovoj konferenciji

456
00:18:47,300 --> 00:18:48,140
 prošle godine

457
00:18:48,140 --> 00:18:49,960
 i onda je se oključio

458
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:50,860
 Matija Ricov,

459
00:18:51,140 --> 00:18:52,060
 Don Davor Klečina

460
00:18:52,060 --> 00:18:52,860
 i Bruno Penava

461
00:18:52,860 --> 00:18:53,560
 da mi pomognu.

462
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:55,520
 Ja stvarno ne poznajem

463
00:18:55,520 --> 00:18:56,800
 povijest Bosne i Hercegovine,

464
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:57,400
 meni je žao.

465
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:58,760
 Ne poznajem

466
00:18:58,760 --> 00:18:59,640
 čak ni u ratu

467
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:00,860
 šta je sad događalo

468
00:19:00,860 --> 00:19:01,960
 i to mi je žao.

469
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:03,400
 Ja sam samo dobio

470
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,020
 pocaj

471
00:19:04,020 --> 00:19:04,940
 da nosim križ

472
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:06,540
 i ja sam se usmjerio

473
00:19:06,540 --> 00:19:06,900
 na to,

474
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:08,340
 ali meni su trebali

475
00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:08,740
 ljudi

476
00:19:08,740 --> 00:19:09,700
