1050
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:28,220
 I Bogu hvala što je odgovorila.

1051
00:31:28,220 --> 00:31:30,340
 Jako je bitno odgovorna poticaj.

1052
00:31:30,340 --> 00:31:34,060
 Naravno, nije lako uočiti Boži poticaj,

1053
00:31:34,060 --> 00:31:36,020
 jer uvijek se umješa tu

1054
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:38,020
 malo našeg, malo zloduha,

1055
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:39,080
 ali kažem,

1056
00:31:39,080 --> 00:31:41,260
 uz poslušnost duhovniku,

1057
00:31:41,260 --> 00:31:43,180
 uz iskreno osluškivanje,

1058
00:31:43,180 --> 00:31:44,560
 razmatranje

1059
00:31:44,560 --> 00:31:46,900
 i uz ponizno srce i poslušno,

1060
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:48,200
 Bog će da blagoslove.

1061
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:51,120
 I sad je uslijedio

1062
00:31:51,120 --> 00:31:53,020
 jedan zanimljiv susret sa jednim srbinom.

1063
00:31:53,020 --> 00:31:54,380
 On se zove Aleksa.

1064
00:31:54,380 --> 00:31:56,440
 Ja sam došao, naravno,

1065
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:59,200
 i u pravoslavni hram da se pomolim.

1066
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:01,160
 Isto tako imao sam susrete

1067
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,140
 i sa hođama,

1068
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:03,880
 sa efendijama.

1069
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:05,420
 Bogu hvala,

1070
00:32:05,420 --> 00:32:07,120
 ovaj križ oprosta su blagoslovila

1071
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:09,440
 i sva tri aktivna biskupa u Bosni i Hercegovini

1072
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:11,060
 i kardinal Vinko Puljč,

1073
00:32:11,060 --> 00:32:12,620
 koji me je vjenčao prije tri tjedna.

1074
00:32:12,620 --> 00:32:14,060
 I Bogu hvala,

1075
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:15,500
 evo, imao sam susrete

1076
00:32:15,500 --> 00:32:17,960
 i sa pravoslavnim sveštenicima,

1077
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,700
 i sa ljudima iz Srbije također.

1078
00:32:19,700 --> 00:32:20,880
 I tu je bio jedan čovjek

1079
00:32:21,120 --> 00:32:22,480
 u jednom hramu

1080
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:23,640
 koji održava taj hram.

1081
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:25,380
 On nije pravoslavni sveštenik,

1082
00:32:25,380 --> 00:32:26,560
 ali održava hram.

1083
00:32:26,560 --> 00:32:27,620
 Zove se Aleksa.

1084
00:32:27,620 --> 00:32:28,980
 Prekrasan čovjek.

1085
00:32:28,980 --> 00:32:31,700
 I dolazim ja sa svojim čačom.

1086
00:32:31,700 --> 00:32:33,720
 Moj čača me tada pratio.

1087
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:35,840
 Nije tada niko zna za mene.

1088
00:32:35,840 --> 00:32:37,100
 Čača krenuo sa mnom.

1089
00:32:37,100 --> 00:32:38,060
 Znam se koji kralj.

1090
00:32:38,060 --> 00:32:38,920
 Koji kralj.

1091
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:42,320
 I dolazimo mi u pravoslavni hram

1092
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:43,420
 i govoro ja o tom Aleksi.

1093
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:45,760
 Mogu li se ja pomoliti ovdje?

1094
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:47,420
 Govorio, on može.

1095
00:32:47,420 --> 00:32:48,520
 Govorio ja,

1096
00:32:48,520 --> 00:32:50,320
 ali prvo mi reci šta je se ovdje dogodilo.

1097
00:32:51,780 --> 00:32:52,540
 Govorio, on.

1098
00:32:52,540 --> 00:32:55,660
 Žao mi je što ti ovo moram reći,

1099
00:32:55,660 --> 00:32:56,080
 ali evo.

1100
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:57,840
 Istina je takva.

1101
00:32:57,840 --> 00:33:00,100
 Ovdje su Hrvati

1102
00:33:00,100 --> 00:33:02,400
 ubili puno srpskog stanovništa.

1103
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:04,380
 Između ostalog i djece.

1104
00:33:04,380 --> 00:33:07,620
 I meni ko Hrvatu stvarno

1105
00:33:07,620 --> 00:33:09,460
 nije mi to bilo baš ugodno čuti.

1106
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:11,400
 Ali bilo je svega.

1107
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:14,560
 Bilo je svega sa sva tri naroda.

1108
00:33:14,560 --> 00:33:16,320
 Negdje su Srbi ubili Hrvati,

1109
00:33:16,320 --> 00:33:17,460
 negdje Hrvati Srbe.

1110
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:18,460
 Bilo je svega.

1111
00:33:18,460 --> 00:33:20,660
 Ja sam sad došao na takvo mjesto.

1112
00:33:21,600 --> 00:33:23,080
 I stvarno mi nije to bilo ugodno čuti,

1113
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:23,520
 ali evo,

1114
00:33:23,520 --> 00:33:25,800
 odlučio sam se poniziti

1115
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:26,800
 i zatražiti oprost.

1116
00:33:26,800 --> 00:33:28,380
 I baš mi je došlo u srce

1117
00:33:28,380 --> 00:33:29,840
 da Bog želi da kleknem

1118
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:31,200
 ispred ikone.

1119
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:31,880
 Evo,

1120
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,040
 kao ova ikona.

1121
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,240
 Baš zanimljivo.

1122
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:34,720
 Slična.

1123
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:38,100
 i došlo mi je da kažem ove riječi.

1124
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:40,000
 Oče nebeski,

1125
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:40,860
 u ime Isusovo,

1126
00:33:40,860 --> 00:33:42,640
 po sili i snazi Duha Svetoga,

1127
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:45,320
 ja kao pojedinac iz Hrvatskog naroda

1128
00:33:45,320 --> 00:33:47,560
 se kajem za sve one zločine

1129
00:33:47,560 --> 00:33:50,120
 koje su pojedinci u Hrvatskom narodu

1130
00:33:50,120 --> 00:33:52,380
 učinili srpskom stanovništvu.

1131
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,320
 I molim za oprost.

1132
00:33:54,320 --> 00:33:58,980
 I kad sam ja to izgovorio,

1133
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:02,620
 taj čovjek je bio baš sretan.

1134
00:34:02,620 --> 00:34:04,440
 Bio je radostan.

1135
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:06,840
 On to možda nije neočekivo.

1136
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:09,280
 Dolazi čovjek sa križem od metar,

1137
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:11,000
 prvi puga vidi u životu,

1138
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:13,360
 a možda sam ja i prvi Hrvat

1139
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,900
 koji je tu došao,

1140
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:17,260
 pokajo se, ponizio

1141
00:34:17,260 --> 00:34:18,240
 i zatraži oprost.

1142
00:34:18,240 --> 00:34:20,420
 Vjerujte mi,

1143
00:34:20,420 --> 00:34:21,860
 ja sam vidio na njemu

1144
00:34:21,860 --> 00:34:24,560
 da je se u njemu dogodilo jedno ozdravljenje,

1145
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:25,600
 a i u meni isto.

1146
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:28,780
 Jer čita život mi se predstavljaju drugi

1147
00:34:28,780 --> 00:34:30,300
 kao neka opasnost,

1148
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:32,340
 a svi smo ljubljena djeca Božja.

1149
00:34:32,340 --> 00:34:35,040
 I nakon toga on dolazi do mene i kaže

1150
00:34:35,040 --> 00:34:37,140
 Jospe, hvala ti puno za molitvu,

1151
00:34:37,140 --> 00:34:38,720
 vidi se da je iz srca.

1152
00:34:38,720 --> 00:34:41,640
 Molim te, kad završi križni put,

1153
00:34:41,640 --> 00:34:42,720
 dođi opet.

1154
00:34:42,720 --> 00:34:44,600
 I ja zagrli njega,

1155
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:45,540
 on mene.

1156
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:47,980
 I tu je se dogodilo jedno ozdravljenje

1157
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:50,760
 i pomerenje između Hrvata i Srbina.

1158
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:53,780
 Bog je bio presretan.

1159
00:34:53,780 --> 00:34:56,960
 Bog je tada bio presretan,

1160
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:59,540
 jer upravo on to želi u Bosni i Hercegovini.

1161
00:34:59,540 --> 00:35:00,620
 Želi oprost.

1162
00:35:00,620 --> 00:35:03,260
 Da je ovo bio križ provokacije,

1163
00:35:03,260 --> 00:35:04,540
 vjerujte mi,

1164
00:35:04,540 --> 00:35:07,060
 mene bi išamarali i jedni i drugi i treći.

1165
00:35:07,060 --> 00:35:10,240
 Da je ovo bio križ provokacije,

1166
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:12,460
 ali pošto je ovo bio križ oprosta,

1167
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:18,320
 a najveća Božja osobina je upraštanje i najljepša,

1168
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:22,260
 tada je Bog pokorio zlo i otvorio svima srce.

1169
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:26,860
 Otvorio je srce i pravoslavcima i muslimanima i katolicima

1170
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:30,240
 da prihvate križ kao simbol pomirenja.

1171
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:34,160
 Vjerujte mi,

1172
00:35:34,160 --> 00:35:37,500
 kada sam vidio da se širi taj požar ljubavi,

1173
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:40,580
 kada sam vidio da gdje god dođem sa križem,

1174
00:35:40,580 --> 00:35:41,980
 da je križ dobro došao,

1175
00:35:41,980 --> 00:35:44,360
 da je prihvaćen i da ima silu i snagu,

1176
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,960
 baš sam bio radostan.

1177
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,340
 Sjećam se u jednom trenutku,

1178
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:49,680
 dolazi jedna muslimanka u Sarajevu

1179
00:35:49,680 --> 00:35:50,620
 i pita me,

1180
00:35:50,620 --> 00:35:51,260
 gdje ti je krst?

1181
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:52,920
 Gdje je krst?

1182
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:56,040
 A men taman tada došla obitelj

1183
00:35:56,040 --> 00:35:58,240
 i ja ostavio križ malo kod obitelji.

1184
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,960
 I govori ona,

1185
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,980
 želim se uskat sa krstom.

1186
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,880
 Govori ja stvarno.

1187
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:04,740
 Govori ona,

1188
00:36:04,740 --> 00:36:06,480
 da, želim se uskat sa krstom.

1189
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:09,540
 I ja donio križ.

1190
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:12,120
 Muslimanka stvarno,

1191
00:36:12,120 --> 00:36:12,320
 evo,

1192
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,520
 bila je u hijabu,

1193
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:15,260
 baš otvorila je srce

1194
00:36:15,260 --> 00:36:17,320
 za simbol pomirenje.

1195
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:20,080
 Dolazi također jedan musliman,

1196
00:36:20,080 --> 00:36:22,060
 mrcina dva metra stoki

1197
00:36:22,060 --> 00:36:24,140
 ili domene u jednom je gradu

1198
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:24,840
 i kaže,

1199
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:25,320
 Jospe,

1200
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,640
 ja imam samo jednu želju.

1201
00:36:26,640 --> 00:36:27,880
 Govori ja koju?

1202
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:31,240
 Koju želim se uskat sa krstom.

1203
00:36:31,240 --> 00:36:32,380
 I on isto.

1204
00:36:32,380 --> 00:36:34,220
 I kad sam vidio

1205
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:36,280
 da i predstavnici drugih religija

1206
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:37,820
 otvraju srce za ovaj križ,

1207
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:40,500
 znao sam da on ima posebnu snagu.

1208
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:44,340
 Ovaj križ je noslo preko tišću ljudi

1209
00:36:44,340 --> 00:36:45,760
 kroz cijelu u Bosni i Hercegovini.

1210
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:48,380
 Poljubilo ga je preko 3-4 tisuće ljudi.

1211
00:36:48,380 --> 00:36:53,140
 I stvarno je zapalio

1212
00:36:53,140 --> 00:36:55,820
 jedan požar ljubavi u Bosni i Hercegovini.

1213
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:57,220
 I kada mi je Mišo rekao

1214
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,620
 da je sada duhovno stanje

1215
00:36:58,620 --> 00:36:59,800
 u Bosni i Hercegovini

1216
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:01,360
 mirnije i drugačije nego prije,

1217
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:03,060
 moram priznat da sam ponosan.

1218
00:37:03,060 --> 00:37:05,660
 Nisam ja neki svetac,

1219
00:37:05,660 --> 00:37:08,420
 nisam ja neki izabran posebno čovjek.

1220
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:11,000
 Vidjeli ste da sam se raspuo ovdje kad sam došao.

1221
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:13,060
 Znači raspuo sam se.

1222
00:37:13,060 --> 00:37:15,320
 Ja sam običan čovjek.

1223
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:19,060
 Pun mana i slabosti.

1224
00:37:19,060 --> 00:37:19,800
 Kao i svi mi.

1225
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:22,180
 Ali crkva je zajednica grešnika

1226
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:24,040
 i Bog poziva grešnike

1227
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:26,260
 da ga slijede.

1228
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:29,940
 Ja vjerujem da će Bog i danas

1229
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:31,060
 i da je jučer učinio

1230
00:37:31,060 --> 00:37:32,460
 puno prekrasnih stvari

1231
00:37:32,460 --> 00:37:35,180
 i dao mnoge plodove i pocaje u vašem srcu.

1232
00:37:35,180 --> 00:37:37,620
 Ne mora svak uzeti doslovno križ

1233
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:38,960
 i nositi ga po svojoj zemlji.

1234
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,660
 Ako bude i takvi pocaje,

1235
00:37:40,660 --> 00:37:41,340
 a Bogu hvala.

1236
00:37:41,340 --> 00:37:44,000
 Evo, Jim je to osje doćeo prošle godine.

1237
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,200
 Meni je došlo.

1238
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:47,180
 Na kraju je bila Božja volja.

1239
00:37:47,180 --> 00:37:49,220
 Da je meni rekao biskup,

1240
00:37:49,220 --> 00:37:50,280
 Jospe, nemoj to rad.

1241
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:51,600
 Ja bi bio poslušan.

1242
00:37:52,100 --> 00:37:53,460
 Jer ja ne želim ovo rad

1243
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:54,620
 bez svoje crkve.

1244
00:37:54,620 --> 00:37:56,880
 Ti ste zarčnik,

1245
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:58,240
 a crkva je zarčnica.

1246
00:37:58,240 --> 00:37:59,780
 Dosta mi je devijacija.

1247
00:37:59,780 --> 00:38:02,340
 Dosta mi je u životu lutanja.

1248
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:04,560
 Puno godina sam proveo

1249
00:38:04,560 --> 00:38:05,480
 u teškom grijehu.

1250
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:07,280
 Želim stvarno biti ponizan

1251
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:08,020
 i poslušan

1252
00:38:08,020 --> 00:38:09,060
 i u spratnju

1253
00:38:09,060 --> 00:38:10,560
 i biskupa i duhovnika

1254
00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:12,080
 slijediti Božje pocaje.

1255
00:38:12,080 --> 00:38:14,440
 Jako je bitna ta poslušnost

1256
00:38:14,440 --> 00:38:15,700
 i zajedništvo sa crkvom.

1257
00:38:15,700 --> 00:38:17,020
 I Bogu hvala

1258
00:38:17,020 --> 00:38:18,180
 na našim svećenicima.

1259
00:38:18,180 --> 00:38:21,360
 Sad ću vam reći par neki smiješnih scena.

1260
00:38:21,700 --> 00:38:22,400
 da ne bi zaspali.

1261
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:25,560
 Kad sam došao u jedno mjesto

1262
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:26,600
 u Bosni i Hercegovini,

1263
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:29,260
 dolazi jedna romkinja do mene

1264
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:31,540
 i kaže

1265
00:38:31,540 --> 00:38:33,260
 Ćao ba,

1266
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:34,340
 pretinite na TikToku.

1267
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:37,800
 govori ja stvarno.

1268
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:38,980
 Govori ona je,

1269
00:38:38,980 --> 00:38:39,780
 jebla, dobar si.

1270
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:41,700
 Govori ja, hvala ti.

1271
00:38:41,700 --> 00:38:42,680
 Govori ona,

1272
00:38:42,680 --> 00:38:43,620
 jebla, zapratim,

1273
00:38:43,620 --> 00:38:44,380
 ja sam Bosanka.

1274
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:47,620
 U Brčko mi došli,

1275
00:38:47,620 --> 00:38:49,000
 ja i Matija,

1276
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:49,660
 svega ovdje,

1277
00:38:49,660 --> 00:38:50,820
 prekrasan čovjek,

1278
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:52,360
 drago mi je da je tu s nama.

1279
00:38:52,900 --> 00:38:53,800
 došli mi u Brčko

1280
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:56,320
 i sada šetamo kroz centar

1281
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:58,340
 i dva Roma,

1282
00:38:58,340 --> 00:38:59,960
 možda četrnec godina.

1283
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:01,700
 Dolaze do nas

1284
00:39:01,700 --> 00:39:03,600
 i motaju se oko križa.

1285
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:06,120
 Dva Roma od četrnec godina.

1286
00:39:06,600 --> 00:39:08,080
 i vidi ja gledaj oni u križ.

1287
00:39:08,080 --> 00:39:09,380
 I govori ja,

1288
00:39:09,380 --> 00:39:10,320
 je li vam fin križ?

1289
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,360
 Gleda ovaj jedan,

1290
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:14,400
 gleda,

1291
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:15,340
 gleda,

1292
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:17,060
 vidi ode Isusa,

1293
00:39:17,060 --> 00:39:17,980
 šta će Isusa ode,

1294
00:39:17,980 --> 00:39:18,860
 jadan apačen,

1295
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:21,320
 satran od bolova.

1296
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:23,520
 Gleda ga on,

1297
00:39:23,520 --> 00:39:24,160
 gleda,

1298
00:39:24,160 --> 00:39:24,820
 gleda,

1299
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:25,380
 gleda

1300
00:39:25,380 --> 00:39:26,060
 i kaže

1301
00:39:26,060 --> 00:39:28,780
 je smršo.

1302
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:38,700
 dolazi ja u Jablancu,

1303
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:40,480
 staje neki džip,

1304
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:41,840
 mrcna neka,

1305
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:43,300
 stok ili brada,

1306
00:39:43,300 --> 00:39:45,120
 zlatni lančić oko vrata,

1307
00:39:45,120 --> 00:39:47,640
 otvara prozor,

1308
00:39:47,640 --> 00:39:49,020
 ja kontak gotovo,

1309
00:39:49,020 --> 00:39:49,980
 evo nisu me,

1310
00:39:49,980 --> 00:39:52,060
 nisu me riješili u Mostaru,

1311
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:53,120
 riješi me u Jablancu.

1312
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:55,540
 Ali prekrasan čovjek na kraju,

1313
00:39:55,540 --> 00:39:58,200
 kako je loša imat neke predrasude.

1314
00:39:58,200 --> 00:40:00,860
 Otvara on prozor od džipa

1315
00:40:00,860 --> 00:40:01,420
 i kaže

1316
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:02,440
 Jospe,

1317
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:04,420
 bošnjak musliman,

1318
00:40:04,420 --> 00:40:06,200
 govori ja rec prijatelju,

1319
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:07,240
 govori ja on,

1320
00:40:07,240 --> 00:40:09,980
 dira li teko?

1321
00:40:09,980 --> 00:40:15,940
 Govori ja nije,

1322
00:40:15,940 --> 00:40:16,220
 brat,

1323
00:40:16,220 --> 00:40:18,540
 ali me šini da bi ti mogo.

1324
00:40:18,540 --> 00:40:21,820
 Nisam to rekao,

1325
00:40:21,820 --> 00:40:22,740
 ali to sam razmišljao.

1326
00:40:22,740 --> 00:40:24,960
 Govori ja on,

1327
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:25,420
 slušaj,

1328
00:40:25,420 --> 00:40:27,220
 ako te neko bude dira,

1329
00:40:27,220 --> 00:40:29,120
 sami javi.

1330
00:40:29,120 --> 00:40:31,800
 Govori ja dobro.

1331
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:32,700
 Govori ja on,

1332
00:40:32,700 --> 00:40:33,520
 piš broj.

1333
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:38,260
 ja mislim da ga isam,

1334
00:40:38,260 --> 00:40:39,080
 možda imam na niku.

1335
00:40:39,080 --> 00:40:41,320
 I zapisao ja broj,

1336
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:41,960
 govori ja dobro,

1337
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:42,980
 kako ću pisat?

1338
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:43,460
 Govori je on,

1339
00:40:43,460 --> 00:40:45,340
 Sancho.

1340
00:40:45,340 --> 00:40:48,700
 Sancho.

1341
00:40:48,700 --> 00:40:50,260
 Hvala Sanchi,

1342
00:40:50,260 --> 00:40:51,080
 Boga blagoslovio.

1343
00:40:51,080 --> 00:40:53,280
 Što se brine za mene.

1344
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:56,280
 I bila jedna scena

1345
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:58,320
 u jednom gradu

1346
00:40:58,320 --> 00:40:59,340
 u Bosni i Hercegovini,

1347
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:04,780
 gdje je jedan momak

1348
00:41:04,780 --> 00:41:06,000
 psovo na mene.

1349
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:08,100
 Psovo na mene

1350
00:41:08,100 --> 00:41:10,100
 i baš je onako bio ljut.

1351
00:41:10,100 --> 00:41:11,500
 Ali taj momak,

1352
00:41:11,500 --> 00:41:12,000
 vidi se,

1353
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,580
 ima oko 17-18 godina,

1354
00:41:13,580 --> 00:41:14,800
 dečkoj u pubertetu.

1355
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:19,120
 I kada su to vidjeli ljudi

1356
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:19,920
 oko njega,

1357
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:21,480
 ljudi u tom gradu,

1358
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:24,720
 nisu to mogli vjerovat.

1359
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,820
 da psuje na mene,

1360
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:27,960
 a nosim križ

1361
00:41:27,960 --> 00:41:28,820
 kroz njihov grad.

1362
00:41:28,820 --> 00:41:30,760
 A tada se već proširila priča

1363
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,740
 da dolazim u miru.

1364
00:41:31,740 --> 00:41:34,180
 I to su vidjela tri momka

1365
00:41:34,180 --> 00:41:36,860
 od možda 30 godina.

1366
00:41:36,860 --> 00:41:39,420
 I ništa ja sam to zanemario.

1367
00:41:39,420 --> 00:41:41,080
 Znao sam ja da bi moglo bit

1368
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:42,660
 nekih određenih komentara

1369
00:41:42,660 --> 00:41:43,920
 i tako.

1370
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,620
 Iako stvarno ih nije bilo puno.

1371
00:41:45,620 --> 00:41:46,560
 Vjerujte mi,

1372
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:49,020
 od deset tišća susreta s ljudima.

1373
00:41:49,020 --> 00:41:50,500
 Imao sam možda pet

1374
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:51,800
 neugodnih iskustava.

1375
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:53,800
 I to je bilo ono,

1376
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:54,920
 vidi budale.

1377
00:41:55,340 --> 00:41:57,080
 Brate, to bi mi možda rekli

1378
00:41:57,080 --> 00:41:57,960
 i moji.

1379
00:41:57,960 --> 00:42:03,280
 Jer ono, nije baš običajeno

1380
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,300
 da nosiš križ

1381
00:42:04,300 --> 00:42:06,080
 kroz Bosnu i Hercegonu.

1382
00:42:06,080 --> 00:42:06,920
 Iako naravno,

1383
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,940
 moja biter me stvarno podržala

1384
00:42:08,940 --> 00:42:10,460
 i zahvalan sam im neizmjerno.

1385
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:11,640
 I ponosni su sada

1386
00:42:11,640 --> 00:42:12,980
 i evo, Bogu hvala na tome.

1387
00:42:12,980 --> 00:42:14,600
 Ali zanimljivost je

1388
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:16,540
 kada je taj dečko psovo na mene,

1389
00:42:16,540 --> 00:42:20,360
 ja sam otišao u samostan,

1390
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:21,440
 tu večer sam spavao

1391
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,280
 kod jednog afratra u samostanu

1392
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:24,980
 i nakon sada vremena

1393
00:42:24,980 --> 00:42:26,380
 dolaze tri momka,

1394
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:27,000
 kucaju,

1395
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,600
 kucaju

1396
00:42:28,600 --> 00:42:30,260
 na vrata samostana

1397
00:42:30,260 --> 00:42:31,840
 i traže Jospa.

1398
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:33,520
 Ja izlazim

1399
00:42:33,520 --> 00:42:34,980
 i govore oni meni.

1400
00:42:34,980 --> 00:42:36,720
 Kaže, Jospe, oprosti,

1401
00:42:36,720 --> 00:42:38,720
 ovo nije prava slika

1402
00:42:38,720 --> 00:42:39,620
 našeg grada.

1403
00:42:39,620 --> 00:42:41,660
 Oprosti nam puno.

1404
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:43,780
 Tri momka od 30 godina

1405
00:42:43,780 --> 00:42:45,400
 dolaze u poniznosti,

1406
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,040
 raskajani

1407
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:46,800
 i kaže,

1408
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:47,940
 ovo nije prava slika

1409
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:48,800
 našeg grada,

1410
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,300
 ti si ovdje dobrodošao.

1411
00:42:50,860 --> 00:42:53,040
 Vjerujte me da ta njihova poniznost

1412
00:42:53,040 --> 00:42:54,720
 i to njihovo zajedništo

1413
00:42:54,720 --> 00:42:55,520
 u poniznosti

1414
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:56,940
 me je toliko dodirnulo

1415
00:42:56,940 --> 00:42:58,160
 da sam bio oduševljen.

1416
00:42:58,160 --> 00:43:00,040
 Bog je blagoslovio.

1417
00:43:00,040 --> 00:43:02,440
 Nakon toga je oslijedio

1418
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:03,680
 zenički zatvor.

1419
00:43:03,680 --> 00:43:05,480
 Baš sam imao želju

1420
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:06,980
 da odem u zenički zatvor.

1421
00:43:08,140 --> 00:43:09,280
 Dobro, ovo sam malo zvuči.

1422
00:43:09,280 --> 00:43:11,860
 Malo zvuči.

1423
00:43:11,860 --> 00:43:13,040
 Nemojte doslovno sveti.

1424
00:43:13,040 --> 00:43:14,840
 Uglavnom imao sam želju

1425
00:43:14,840 --> 00:43:16,300
 da posjetim zatvorenike.

1426
00:43:16,300 --> 00:43:19,360
 Znam da Isus ima posebno

1427
00:43:19,360 --> 00:43:21,600
 milosrđe za ljude

1428
00:43:21,600 --> 00:43:22,940
 koji su posebno ranjeni.

1429
00:43:22,940 --> 00:43:25,420
 A kada neko učini

1430
00:43:25,420 --> 00:43:26,540
 neko veliko zlo,

1431
00:43:26,540 --> 00:43:28,540
 često to bude plod

1432
00:43:28,540 --> 00:43:29,840
 duboke ranjenosti

1433
00:43:29,840 --> 00:43:31,720
 koju su ti ljudi

1434
00:43:31,720 --> 00:43:32,900
 doživjeli u djetinstvu.

1435
00:43:32,900 --> 00:43:35,500
 I baš sam nekako htio

1436
00:43:35,500 --> 00:43:37,080
 da im Bog iskaže milosrđe.

1437
00:43:37,860 --> 00:43:38,500
 I Bogu hvala,

1438
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:39,260
 Bog mi je providio

1439
00:43:39,260 --> 00:43:40,680
 preko jednog divnog svećenika

1440
00:43:40,680 --> 00:43:41,300
 u Zenci

1441
00:43:41,300 --> 00:43:43,360
 da dođem do zatvorenika

1442
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:45,000
 i imali smo jedan susret.

1443
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:46,340
 I to je bilo prekrasno.

1444
00:43:46,340 --> 00:43:48,040
 Bio je katolički svećenik,

1445
00:43:48,040 --> 00:43:49,460
 bio je hođa

1446
00:43:49,460 --> 00:43:51,240
 i bio je pravoslavni sveštenik.

1447
00:43:51,240 --> 00:43:52,440
 I ja.

1448
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:54,600
 I naravno direktor zatvora

1449
00:43:54,600 --> 00:43:55,460
 i ostali ljudi.

1450
00:43:55,460 --> 00:43:56,940
 I sad je tu došlo

1451
00:43:56,940 --> 00:43:58,320
 trice zatvorenika.

1452
00:43:58,320 --> 00:44:00,560
 Baš su bili onako izmješani

1453
00:44:00,560 --> 00:44:02,340
 bošnjaci, Srbiji i Hrvati.

1454
00:44:02,340 --> 00:44:04,340
 I oni su se sad poredali

1455
00:44:04,340 --> 00:44:06,720
 ispred mene

1456
00:44:06,720 --> 00:44:07,580
 i meni je rekao direktor

1457
00:44:07,580 --> 00:44:08,240
 zatvora.

1458
00:44:08,240 --> 00:44:09,720
 Jospe, imaš 15 minuta.

1459
00:44:09,720 --> 00:44:11,140
 Govori ja, dobro.

1460
00:44:11,140 --> 00:44:12,760
 I meni je došlo srce

1461
00:44:12,760 --> 00:44:14,020
 da Isus želi samo ovo.

1462
00:44:14,020 --> 00:44:15,420
 Da je im pričan

1463
00:44:15,420 --> 00:44:16,440
 o milosrđu.

1464
00:44:16,440 --> 00:44:19,080
 O milosrđu.

1465
00:44:21,220 --> 00:44:23,120
 U privatnoj objavi dnevnika

1466
00:44:23,120 --> 00:44:24,660
 svete Faustine Kovalske

1467
00:44:24,660 --> 00:44:26,460
 Isus govori da oni svećenici

1468
00:44:26,460 --> 00:44:28,100
 koji budu propovjedali

1469
00:44:28,100 --> 00:44:29,160
 njegovo milosrđe,

1470
00:44:29,160 --> 00:44:32,680
 da će Bog posebno pomazat njihove riječi.

1471
00:44:32,680 --> 00:44:35,440
 i da će posebno doticat srca ljudi.

1472
00:44:35,440 --> 00:44:40,200
 I meni je to došlo da kao lajk evangelizator

1473
00:44:40,200 --> 00:44:42,000
 da otvorim srce za Božje milosrđe

1474
00:44:42,000 --> 00:44:44,200
 i da dopustim Bogu da ih ljubi.

1475
00:44:44,900 --> 00:44:47,420
 Jer ti ljudi su odbačeni, ranjeni.

1476
00:44:47,420 --> 00:44:49,720
 A možda su odbačeni i od svoje obitelji.

1477
00:44:49,720 --> 00:44:51,760
 Od svojih najbližijih.

1478
00:44:51,760 --> 00:44:54,000
 I tu su u zatvoru.

1479
00:44:54,000 --> 00:44:54,920
 Iza rešetaka.

1480
00:44:54,920 --> 00:44:56,580
 I

1481
00:44:56,580 --> 00:45:00,180
 meni dolazi samo da im kažem

1482
00:45:00,180 --> 00:45:01,560
 da nijedan grijeh

1483
00:45:01,560 --> 00:45:04,000
 nije veći od Božjeg milosrđa.

1484
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:08,240
 Desni razbojnik

1485
00:45:08,240 --> 00:45:11,820
 u to doba završna križu

1486
00:45:11,820 --> 00:45:13,580
 Isu je završio nevin.

1487
00:45:13,960 --> 00:45:15,660
 Ali ovi drugi koji su završavali

1488
00:45:15,660 --> 00:45:16,820
 nisu bili baš nevinni.

1489
00:45:16,820 --> 00:45:18,600
 Znali su svašta rad.

1490
00:45:18,600 --> 00:45:20,380
 Neki su bili pljačkaši.

1491
00:45:20,380 --> 00:45:21,820
 Neki su možda i ubili nekoga.

1492
00:45:21,820 --> 00:45:24,880
 Desni razbojnik

1493
00:45:24,880 --> 00:45:26,940
 je možda pravedno završio na križu.

1494
00:45:26,940 --> 00:45:29,780
 Ali je se pokajao u zadnjoj sekundi svoga života.

1495
00:45:29,780 --> 00:45:31,560
 Isu mu kaže

1496
00:45:31,560 --> 00:45:33,120
 još danas ćeš biti sa mnom u raju.

1497
00:45:33,120 --> 00:45:35,760
 I rekao sam zatvorenicima

1498
00:45:35,760 --> 00:45:38,180
 pogledajte tog desnog razbojnika.

1499
00:45:38,180 --> 00:45:39,300
 I on je razbojnik.

1500
00:45:39,300 --> 00:45:41,220
 I on je možda bio u zatvoru.

1501
00:45:41,220 --> 00:45:43,180
 Ali je danas

1502
00:45:43,180 --> 00:45:44,320
 sa Bogom u nebu.

1503
00:45:44,320 --> 00:45:46,540
 Niste izgubljeni.

1504
00:45:46,540 --> 00:45:47,880
 Ima nade i za vas.

1505
00:45:47,880 --> 00:45:49,120
 I vjerujte mi

1506
00:45:49,120 --> 00:45:51,500
 to je toliko dodirilo

1507
00:45:51,500 --> 00:45:52,560
 neke od njih

1508
00:45:52,560 --> 00:45:53,580
 da je jedan

1509
00:45:53,580 --> 00:45:54,340
 koji je

1510
00:45:54,340 --> 00:45:55,280
 među

1511
00:45:55,280 --> 00:45:56,760
 najhiperaktivnijim

1512
00:45:56,760 --> 00:45:58,620
 blagorečeno u zatvoru

1513
00:45:58,620 --> 00:45:59,360
 se ustao

1514
00:45:59,360 --> 00:46:00,440
 nakon toga i rekao

1515
00:46:00,440 --> 00:46:02,300
 mogli ja nešto reći?

1516
00:46:02,300 --> 00:46:04,220
 Govori on mi.

1517
00:46:04,220 --> 00:46:05,300
 Može naravno.

1518
00:46:05,300 --> 00:46:06,300
 I govori on

1519
00:46:06,300 --> 00:46:06,760
 Josipa Josipe

1520
00:46:06,760 --> 00:46:08,720
 hvala ti puno

1521
00:46:08,720 --> 00:46:10,440
 hvala ti puno

1522
00:46:10,440 --> 00:46:11,660
 što nas ne gledaš

1523
00:46:11,660 --> 00:46:12,560
 ko kriminalce

1524
00:46:12,560 --> 00:46:14,380
 nego ko Božju djecu.

1525
00:46:14,380 --> 00:46:18,040
 Vjerujte mi da sam se naježio

1526
00:46:18,040 --> 00:46:19,440
 kad je on to rekao.

1527
00:46:19,440 --> 00:46:20,860
 Nakon toga

1528
00:46:20,860 --> 00:46:22,740
 petorica žele ljubit križ.

1529
00:46:24,020 --> 00:46:24,980
 Petorica kažu

1530
00:46:24,980 --> 00:46:26,200
 mi želimo poljubit križ.

1531
00:46:26,200 --> 00:46:28,380
 Ja iznosim križ

1532
00:46:28,380 --> 00:46:29,560
 i oni ga ljube.

1533
00:46:29,560 --> 00:46:31,800
 Jedan dolazi

1534
00:46:31,800 --> 00:46:32,980
 daje mi kruncu.

1535
00:46:32,980 --> 00:46:35,580
 I nakon toga

1536
00:46:35,580 --> 00:46:36,760
 govori direktor

1537
00:46:36,760 --> 00:46:38,300
 želite li se uskat sa Josipom

1538
00:46:38,300 --> 00:46:40,180
 a oni se inače ne vole slikat.

1539
00:46:40,180 --> 00:46:41,920
 Ko se voli slikat

1540
00:46:41,920 --> 00:46:42,800
 u zatvoru

1541
00:46:42,800 --> 00:46:44,000
 još za javnost?

1542
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:48,200
 Zbog svojih najbližih

1543
00:46:48,200 --> 00:46:49,500
 zbog ljudi

1544
00:46:49,500 --> 00:46:50,500
 u selu, u gradovima

1545
00:46:50,500 --> 00:46:51,200
 ko to voli?

1546
00:46:51,200 --> 00:46:52,360
 Ali pasite ovo

1547
00:46:52,360 --> 00:46:54,000
 toliko je njih izdodirno

1548
00:46:54,000 --> 00:46:56,000
 da se svi htjeli uskat

1549
00:46:56,000 --> 00:46:57,200
 sa križem.

1550
00:46:57,200 --> 00:46:59,060
 Samo jedan

1551
00:46:59,060 --> 00:47:00,540
 onako malo je se nečiko

1552
00:47:00,540 --> 00:47:01,560
 ali kad je vidio

1553
00:47:01,560 --> 00:47:02,260
 da će svi onda

1554
00:47:02,260 --> 00:47:02,860
 i on.

1555
00:47:02,860 --> 00:47:05,940
